Package: libpoll
Version: 1.4
Revision: 11
Depends: %N-shlibs (= %v-%r)
Type: nosource
CompileScript: true
InstallScript: <<
  install -d -m 755 %i/lib
  ln -sf /usr/lib/libSystem.dylib %i/lib/libpoll.1.1.dylib
  ln -sf /usr/lib/libSystem.dylib %i/lib/libpoll.1.2.dylib
  ln -sf /usr/lib/libSystem.dylib %i/lib/libpoll.1.3.dylib
  ln -sf /usr/lib/libSystem.dylib %i/lib/libpoll.1.dylib
  install -d -m 755 %i/share/doc/%N
  touch %i/share/doc/%N/.turd
<<
SplitOff: <<
  Package: %N-shlibs
  Description: SysV poll(2) Emulation shared libraries (dummy)
  Files: lib/libpoll.*.dylib
<<
Description: SysV poll(2) Emulation (dummy)
DescDetail: <<
The poll-emulation library is now part of Apple's libSystem.
This package exists only for compatibility with older fink
packages that expect libpoll to be in %p/lib.
